A message for Greeks:
Paidia prospa8w poly na kanw seed ola ayta ta arxeia me mia kwloDSL.
Epeidh einai poly sygkekrimena arxeia poy aforoyn mono to ellhniko koino, einai profanes oti an den ta kanete seed ki eseis, 8a xa8oune.
8a sas parakalousa, afoy ta katebasete na synexisete na ta kanete seed gia ena megalo diasthma, akoma ki an dinete upload mono 1Kb/sec.
8a mou htan poly eykolo na dwsw sto torrent enan tracker pou kanei check ti ratio exeis ki an se bgalei gyfto na se kanei ban.
Protimisa ton TPB epeidh mporeis na eisai leecher xwris upload. To upload to afhsa sto ellhniko sas filotimo.
Eimai sigouros oti 8a antapokri8eite, gia to kalo toy ellhnikou koinou.
Eyxaristw poly.

I'll seed to at least a 2:1 ratio - keep them coming
